      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.Item.iFT8IY1FU4oAh2el]{Bolster Resistances (Ex)}</p>\n<p><span>You can temporarily modify your armor to improve your resistance to energy attacks. As a move action, you can gain resistance 5 to a type of energy damage of your choice until the beginning of your next turn; this does not stack with any other sources of resistance. You can use this ability a number of times per day equal to your Intelligence modifier.</span></p>\n<p><em>When applying the Effect: Bolster Resistances (Ex) be sure to select and enable the desired energy resistance under the Modifiers tab.</em></p>"
